room_title: Escape room "Voices" by Twisted Exit in Lancaster (CA)
room_description: 30 years ago, the Richardsons moved into this house only to be driven away by pure evil. Upon putting boxes in the attic, the youngest child Evilyn stumbled across a beautiful doll. in the weeks following their move into the new home, the family started being terrorized by a spirit trapped in the doll. Fed up, Evilyn's parents decided to throw away the doll but soon realized they had made a grave mistake...
